 der Bewegung nach. Das Buch legt anhand empirischer Daten aus einer multilokalen Feldforschung dar, in welchem Spannungsverhältnis sich soziale Bewegungen heute befinden.  aThe field of tension in which ethnic identity formation lies today is made palpable by this ethnological study through the example of the Amazigh movement in Morocco.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aAfrika. 4aEthnologie. 4aIdentität. 4aKultur. 4aMarokko. 4aSoziale Bewegung. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh  aAfrica.  aCulture.  aEthnology.  aIdentity.  aMorocco.  aSocial Movement.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2015z9783110438741oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPP Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070099208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript: Complete eBook-Package 2014z9783110401226oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/transcript.9783839427811zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839427811423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839427811/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  a978-3-11-070099-2  PP Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DSWb2015  aZDB-23-TGPb2014  aZDB-23-TGPc2014d2016